# AGENTS

## Working Agreement

- Prefer focused edits over broad refactors.
- Keep feature code inside `apps/web/src/features` unless it is genuinely reusable.
- Treat `packages/config-*` as shared infrastructure; update them deliberately.
- Run `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`, and `pnpm test` before claiming a task is complete.
- Update `DESIGN.md` when architecture boundaries or package responsibilities change.
